      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LOTS OF CHANGE (5) is back today after a layoff of eight months. Closed the last preparation in great style with a win by 1.1 metres over 2116m at this track. Sure to prove hard to beat on his return. OLD DOMINION (8) broke in the run and finished a long last when resuming last start over 2116m at this track. No harm in drawing here with the sprint lane to rely upon. Won't find this any harder so he can return to form. MRIYA DREAM (9) is on the radar after his last-start sixth over 2185m at this track a week ago. BEE BEE BEROC (11) found a couple better two runs back then made mistakes last time when he broke and finished 23 metres back in seventh over 2503m at Gloucester Park. May just need a bit of luck at some point from this difficult draw. Meets a similar line up so if he behaves a big run is likely.",
